title: 62. When Life Hands You Lemons + St. Ives... My CRINGIEST Skin Sins.
description:
Hi Roomies!! 

I'm back with a solo ep sharing the cringes things I've ever done to my skin, and reading yours too! Sit back, relax, have a laugh and let's just be happy we have come SO FAR since lemons and St. Ives. Have a topic request or question for a future episode? Comment on my latest @myestytessa.
